# =============================================================================
#  NORTHSTAR CRYPTO — Configuration Template
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
#  cp .env.example .env
# =============================================================================
# STEP 1: Add your exchange API keys (Kraken shown — works with any exchange)
# STEP 2: Add your NVIDIA NIM API key (free at build.nvidia.com)
# STEP 3: Run start_all.bat
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
#  KRAKEN-HYBRAD9 — Config
